::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about Fuli the Remembrance.
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401010653-->
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 144.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' I can give you the memories related to the Aeon, Fuli...
:::::::The girl waved her hand, as if tossing a small pebble that caused the water surface to keep rippling. You suddenly remember&mdash;
:::::::Fuli, the Aeon on the Path of Remembrance, preserves the precious memories of a dying universe for its eventual rebirth... Here, the memories abruptly come to an end.
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 145.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' That's all I have. I don't have the honor of keeping the experience of seeing the Aeon, Fuli with my own eyes.
::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about the Garden of Recollection.
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401010658-->
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 146.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' Huh? I thought I already told you about that. You really are forgetful.
:::::::You suddenly remember what the girl had said, and the words begin ringing in your ears&mdash;
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 109.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' Garden of Recollection is an organization that worships the Aeon Fuli. As a messenger for the Remembrance, we surrendered our worldly bodies and traverse the universe in the form of memes to search the stars on behalf of Fuli for the most precious memories.
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 148.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' Do you remember now?
::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} What is the purpose of collecting memories?
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401010663-->
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 149.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' "The disappearance of those with form will inevitably bring about the obliteration of those without."
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 150.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' Look at the galaxy. After the incident with the Antimatter Legion, civilizations are like dying embers in the wind. Many worlds wither and crumble even without Nanook's influence. It is unacceptable to allow the memories of civilizations to simply vanish.
:::::::{{A|VO SideX sys1 messenger 151.ogg}} '''Messenger:''' That is why Garden of Recollection has decided to collect and safe keep their memories. Once the crisis ends, the fragments of these memories will shape a blueprint of rebirth for everything that has disappeared.
::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About you...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_401010668-->
